trainings.name: Full Body Strength Training
trainings.description: A comprehensive workout to build strength and muscle mass.

exercises.title: Barbell Squats
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, lower the bar onto your upper back, and squat down until your thighs are parallel to the ground.

exercises.title: Push-Ups
exercises.instructions: Place hands shoulder-width apart, lower your chest towards the floor, and push back up.

exercises.title: Pull-Ups
exercises.instructions: Grab a pull-up bar with an overhand grip, hang with arms fully extended, and pull yourself up until your chin is over the bar.

exercises.title: Dumbbell Rows
exercises.instructions: Hinge at your hips, keep your back straight, and pull the dumbbells towards your chest.

exercises.title: Overhead Press
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, hold dumbbells at shoulder height, and press them straight up overhead.

trainings.name: Yoga for Flexibility
trainings.description: Improve your flexibility and range of motion with this yoga flow.

exercises.title: Downward Dog
exercises.instructions: Start on all fours, lift your hips up and back, forming an inverted V-shape with your body.

exercises.title: Warrior II Pose
exercises.instructions: Step your feet wide apart, turn your right foot out, and bend your right knee.

exercises.title: Triangle Pose
exercises.instructions: From Warrior II, straighten your right leg and reach your right hand forward.

exercises.title: Pigeon Pose
exercises.instructions: Bring your right shin forward and your left leg back, resting on your hips.

exercises.title: Child's Pose
exercises.instructions: Kneel on the floor, bring your big toes together, and rest your forehead on the ground.

trainings.name: High-Intensity Interval Training (HIIT)
trainings.description: Burn calories and improve your cardiovascular fitness with this HIIT workout.

exercises.title: Burpees
exercises.instructions: Perform a squat, kick your feet back, do a push-up, return to the squat position, and jump up.

exercises.title: Jumping Jacks
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet together, jump while spreading your legs and raising your arms overhead.

exercises.title: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: Start in a plank position and alternate bringing your knees towards your chest.

exercises.title: High Knees
exercises.instructions: Run in place, bringing your knees up high towards your chest.

exercises.title: Plank
exercises.instructions: Hold your body in a straight line from head to heels, supported by your forearms and toes.

trainings.name: Pilates for Core Strength
trainings.description: Strengthen your core muscles and improve your posture with this Pilates routine.

exercises.title: Hundred
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, lift your legs and head, and pump your arms up and down.

exercises.title: Roll-Up
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, engage your core, and slowly roll up to a seated position.

exercises.title: Teaser
exercises.instructions: Sit with your knees bent, lean back, and lift your legs to a 45-degree angle.

exercises.title: Swimming
exercises.instructions: Lie on your stomach, lift your arms and legs, and alternate lifting your opposite arm and leg.

exercises.title: Bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back, bend your knees, and lift your hips off the ground.

trainings.name: Cardio Kickboxing
trainings.description: Get a great cardio workout while learning basic kickboxing techniques.

exercises.title: Jab
exercises.instructions: Extend your lead arm straight out, rotating your fist so your palm faces down.

exercises.title: Cross
exercises.instructions: Rotate your hips and extend your rear arm across your body.

exercises.title: Hook
exercises.instructions: Pivot on your lead foot and swing your lead arm in a circular motion.

exercises.title: Roundhouse Kick
exercises.instructions: Lift your kicking leg, bend your knee, and swing your leg in a circular motion.

exercises.title: Front Kick
exercises.instructions: Lift your kicking leg and extend it straight out in front of you.

trainings.name: Bodyweight Bootcamp
trainings.description: A challenging workout using only your bodyweight for resistance.

exercises.title: Jumping Lunges
exercises.instructions: Step forward with one leg and lower your body until both knees are bent at a 90-degree angle. Jump explosively and switch legs in the air.

exercises.title: Tricep Dips
exercises.instructions: Place your hands shoulder-width apart on a bench or chair, lower your body by bending your elbows, and push back up.

exercises.title: Plank Jacks
exercises.instructions: Start in a plank position and jump your feet out to the sides and then back together.

exercises.title: Superman
exercises.instructions: Lie on your stomach, lift your arms and legs off the ground, and hold for a few seconds.

exercises.title: Wall Sit
exercises.instructions: Stand with your back against a wall, lower your body until your thighs are parallel to the ground, and hold.

trainings.name: Zumba Dance Fitness
trainings.description: Dance your way to fitness with this fun and energetic Zumba class.

exercises.title: Merengue
exercises.instructions: Step your feet to the side, shifting your weight from one foot to the other.

exercises.title: Salsa
exercises.instructions: Step forward with one foot, then back with the other, adding hip movements.

exercises.title: Cumbia
exercises.instructions: Step to the side, lifting your heels and adding arm movements.

exercises.title: Reggaeton
exercises.instructions: Move your hips and chest to the rhythm, adding steps and jumps.

exercises.title: Belly Dance
exercises.instructions: Isolate and move your hips, chest, and ribcage independently.

trainings.name: Beginner's Running Plan
trainings.description: Start running with this beginner-friendly plan that gradually increases your mileage.

exercises.title: Warm-up Walk
exercises.instructions: Walk at a brisk pace for 5-10 minutes to prepare your body for running.

exercises.title: Run/Walk Intervals
exercises.instructions: Alternate between running for short intervals and walking for recovery.

exercises.title: Cool-down Walk
exercises.instructions: Walk at a relaxed pace for 5-10 minutes to allow your body to cool down.

exercises.title: Stretching
exercises.instructions: Stretch your major muscle groups to improve flexibility and prevent injury.

trainings.name: Strength and Conditioning for Athletes
trainings.description: Improve your athletic performance with this strength and conditioning program.

exercises.title: Box Jumps
exercises.instructions: Stand in front of a box, squat down, and jump explosively onto the box.

exercises.title: Kettlebell Swings
exercises.instructions: Hold a kettlebell with both hands, swing it between your legs, and then up to chest height.

exercises.title: Agility Ladder Drills
exercises.instructions: Perform various footwork drills using an agility ladder to improve speed and coordination.

exercises.title: Medicine Ball Throws
exercises.instructions: Throw a medicine ball against a wall or with a partner to develop power.

exercises.title: Sprints
exercises.instructions: Run as fast as you can for short distances to improve speed and acceleration.

trainings.name: Mindfulness Meditation
trainings.description: Reduce stress and improve your mental well-being with this guided meditation.

exercises.title: Breathing Exercises
exercises.instructions: Focus on your breath, inhaling slowly and deeply, and exhaling fully.

exercises.title: Body Scan Meditation
exercises.instructions: Bring your attention to each part of your body, noticing any sensations.

exercises.title: Loving-Kindness Meditation
exercises.instructions: Cultivate feelings of love and compassion towards yourself and others.

exercises.title: Walking Meditation
exercises.instructions: Walk slowly and mindfully, paying attention to each step and your surroundings.
